# Vendored sprite source — NOT committed (14M). Re-fetch to regenerate sprites:
#   Ninja Adventure (CC0, pixel-boy): clone the pack into assets/ninja-src
#   Sprout Lands Basic (Cup Nooble, non-commercial+credit): into assets/Sprout Lands - Sprites - Basic pack
# Then: python prep_ninja.py  (writes the CC0 sprites below)
assets/

# Only the Ninja-Adventure (CC0) sprites the current renderer uses are committed.
# Everything else in sprites_ready/ is Sprout-Lands-derived scratch (non-commercial
# license — do NOT redistribute) or regenerable, so it stays ignored.
sprites_ready/*
!sprites_ready/grass.png
!sprites_ready/path.png
!sprites_ready/water.png
!sprites_ready/manor.png
!sprites_ready/hut.png
